metadata.name: The Cairngorms
metadata.description:
Cairngorms/Am Monadh Ruadh (The Red Hills)

Area: 292 km2 (113 sq mi)

Location: Eastern Highlands of Scotland

Highest Point: Ben Macdui 1,309 m/ 4,295 ft

Illustrated with 4,800 colored squares of archaic amber-rusted frigid stone, 120 x 40 (2627 x 871 final image)
